Package jetbrains.mps.smodel

Class ModelDependencyScanner

  • java.lang.Object
    • jetbrains.mps.smodel.ModelDependencyScanner
  • public final class ModelDependencyScanner
extends Object
    Facility to collect actual external dependencies, like languages, concepts, and other models for a given model or set of nodes. Walks a model and gathers information about nodes according to configuration. By default, collects languages in use and references to external models. JFI, there's ModelDependencyUpdate in [project] that deals with import changes
